---
title: Creamy Lemon Shrimp Linguine with Bacon and Tomato Blush Sauce
description: This dish combines two Italian classics — shrimp scampi and pasta all'amatriciana — into one irresistible dinner! Imagine garlicky, lemony buttered shrimp tossed with linguine in a rich tomato blush sauce with smoky bacon. Is your mouth watering yet?
